Unit Test Specifications

Multiplication Function

Expect multiplication(2, 3) to be a number
Expect multiplication(2, 3) to be equal to 6
Expect multiplication(-2, 3) to be equal to -6

concatOdds Function

Expect concatOdds([3, 2, 1], [9, 1, 1, 1, 4, 15, -1]) to return [-1, 1, 3, 9, 15]
Expect concatOdds([1, 1, 1], [3, 3, 3]) to return [1, 3]
Expect concatOdds("string", [1, 3]) to be an error

Functional Test Specifications

Shopping Cart Checkout Feature

When a user goes to check out with an empty cart, they should be shown an error message preventing them from continuing
When a user adds items to the cart and goes to checkout, they should be shown a summary of their order
When a user successfully enters valid payment, they should see an order confirmation page
When a user completes a purchase, they should receive an email confirmation

